\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wrench\"><path d=\"M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z\"></path></svg></div>ABC<span class=\"text-accent-500\">Resolve</span></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-6 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600\"><a class=\"hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/#como-funciona\">Como funciona</a><a class=\"hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/#categorias\">Serviços</a><a class=\"hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Pedir orçamento</a></nav><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-3\"><a class=\"btn-accent text-sm py-2\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Solicitar serviço</a><a class=\"btn-secondary text-sm py-2\" href=\"/cadastro-prestador\">Sou prestador</a></div><button class=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-lg text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-100\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></header><main class=\"bg-gray-50 min-h-screen py-12\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-primary-600 mb-6\" href=\"/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg> Voltar</a><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm p-8\"><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6\">Termos de Uso</h1><div class=\"prose prose-sm text-gray-600 space-y-4\"><p>Ao utilizar o ABCResolve, você concorda com os seguintes termos:</p><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 text-base mt-6\">1. Sobre a plataforma</h2><p>O ABCResolve é uma plataforma de conexão entre clientes e prestadores de serviços na região do Grande ABC, São Paulo.</p><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 text-base mt-6\">2. Responsabilidades</h2><p>O ABCResolve atua como intermediário e não se responsabiliza pela execução dos serviços contratados diretamente entre clientes e prestadores.</p><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 text-base mt-6\">3. Dados pessoais</h2><p>Os dados fornecidos são utilizados exclusivamente para conectar clientes e prestadores. Não compartilhamos seus dados com terceiros sem consentimento.</p><h2 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 text-base mt-6\">4. Gratuidade</h2><p>A solicitação de serviços por clientes é totalmente gratuita. Prestadores cadastrados podem estar sujeitos a tarifas futuras mediante aviso prévio.</p></div></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-gray-900 text-gray-300\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-14\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10\"><div class=\"md:col-span-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-extrabold text-xl text-white mb-3\"><div class=\"bg-primary-600 text-white p-1.5 rounded-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wrench\"><path d=\"M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z\"></path></svg></div>ABC<span class=\"text-accent-500\">Resolve</span></div><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed\">Conectamos você aos melhores profissionais da região do Grande ABC.</p><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin text-primary-400\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg>Grande ABC — SP</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-phone text-primary-400\"><path d=\"M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z\"></path></svg>(11) 99999-0000</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail text-primary-400\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"16\" x=\"2\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7\"></path></svg>contato@abcresolve.com.br</div></div></div><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Para Clientes</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/solicitar-servico\">Solicitar serviço</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/#categorias\">Ver categorias</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/#como-funciona\">Como funciona</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/#depoimentos\">Avaliações</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Para Prestadores</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/cadastro-prestador\">Cadastre-se</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/assinatura\">Ativar assinatura</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/#como-funciona\">Como receber pedidos</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Cidades Atendidas</h4><ul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-gray-400\"><li>Santo André</li><li>São Bernardo do Campo</li><li>São Caetano do Sul</li><li>Diadema</li><li>Mauá</li><li>Ribeirão Pires</li><li>Rio Grande da Serra</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-gray-800 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-3 text-xs text-gray-500\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> ABCResolve. Todos os direitos reservados.</p><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/privacidade\">Privacidade</a><a class=\"hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/termos\">Termos de uso</a></div></div></div></footer><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-7f168d1886c817f0.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7555,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[1295,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[4615,[\\\"607\\\",\\\"static/chunks/607-1451ee05c69949dc.js\\\",\\\"831\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/termos/page-9e41e75710a3cd23.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[6874,[\\\"607\\\",\\\"static/chunks/607-1451ee05c69949dc.js\\\",\\\"831\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/termos/page-9e41e75710a3cd23.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:I[9665,[],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\n8:I[9665,